Kutholakale ukuthi othile okade useduze kwakhe une-COVID-19
Njalo lapho othile abelana ngomphumela wokuthi unaso isifo, kungase kusize ukuvimbela esinye isigameko se-COVID-19. Ukwabelana ngomphumela wakho wokuhlolwa ngeke kukudalule kwabanye abantu.

Njengoba iziphathimandla zakho zezempilo zilungisa indlela esiphendula ngayo ku-COVID-19, asisayisekeli le app. Siyabonga ngokusebenzisa i-app kanye nokusiza ukuvikela umphakathi wakho.
